c: 28
v: 82
t: "And those who had coveted his (Korah's) place but yesterday exclaimed the morning after (Korah's sinking), \"Ah, well! Allah gives the provision for living in ample measure to whom He wills of His slaves and restricts it to whom He wills. Had Allah not been gracious to us, He would have sunk the earth with us. Ah, well! Those who suppress the Truth shall not attain salvation"